Symbol.Script_3D:
! Gas Meter
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat HouseMaterial = sMat DialPlateMaterial = sMat WheelMaterial = sMat ENDIF MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
addStatus = 0 IF GLOB_CONTEXT > 40 AND GLOB_CONTEXT < 50 THEN addStatus = 3 ENDIF
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
IF withHouse THEN MATERIAL HouseMaterial
ADDy B/2 ROTx 90 EXTRUDE 5, 0, 0, B, addStatus+16+32, -A/2, 0, 0, A/2, 0, 0, A/2, ZZYZX, 0, -A/2, ZZYZX, 0, -A/2, 0, -1
POLY_ 5, -A/2, 0, 1, A/2, 0, 1, A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, 0, -1
IF isCovered THEN ADDz B POLY_ 5, -A/2, 0, 1, A/2, 0, 1, A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, ZZYZX, 1, -A/2, 0, -1 DEL 1 ENDIF DEL 2
ADDz ZZYZX/2 ELSE ADDz meterBoxSizeZ/2 ENDIF
MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial ADD -meterBoxSizeX/2, -meterBoxSizeY/2, -meterBoxSizeZ/2 IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ADDy chSize BLOCK meterBoxSizeX, meterBoxSizeY-chSize*2, meterBoxSizeZ DEL 1
FOR i = 1 TO 2 MULy 1-2*(i-1) ADD meterBoxSizeX/2, chSize-meterBoxSizeY*(i-1), 0 ROTx 90 RULED 4, 1+2+4+16+32, -meterBoxSizeX/2, 0, 0, meterBoxSizeX/2, 0, 0, meterBoxSizeX/2, meterBoxSizeZ, 0, -meterBoxSizeX/2, meterBoxSizeZ, 0,
-meterBoxSizeX/2+chsize, chsize, chsize, meterBoxSizeX/2-chsize, chsize, chsize, meterBoxSizeX/2-chsize, meterBoxSizeZ-chsize, chsize, -meterBoxSizeX/2+chsize, meterBoxSizeZ-chsize, chsize DEL 3 NEXT i
ww = (meterBoxSizeX - chsize*2)*0.80 hh = (meterBoxSizeZ - chsize*2)*0.40 ADD meterBoxSizeX/2-ww/2, 0, meterBoxSizeZ/2 MATERIAL DialPlateMaterial ROTx 90 ADDz EPS POLY_ 5, 0, 0, 1, ww, 0, 1, ww, hh, 1, 0, hh, 1, 0, 0, -1
MATERIAL WheelMaterial ADD ww*0.1, hh*0.40, EPS ww = ww*0.80 hh = ww*0.20 POLY_ 5, 0, 0, 1, ww, 0, 1, ww, hh, 1, 0, hh, 1, 0, 0, -1 DEL 5 ELSE BLOCK meterBoxSizeX, meterBoxSizeY, meterBoxSizeZ ENDIF DEL 1
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 15, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 15 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Gas Meter
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 !!HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 A/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1
DRAWINDEX 10
PUT meterBoxSizeX/2, meterBoxSizeY/2-chsize, 1, meterBoxSizeX/2-chsize, meterBoxSizeY/2, 1, -meterBoxSizeX/2+chsize, meterBoxSizeY/2, 1, -meterBoxSizeX/2, meterBoxSizeY/2-chsize, 1, -meterBoxSizeX/2, -meterBoxSizeY/2+chsize, 1, -meterBoxSizeX/2+chsize, -meterBoxSizeY/2, 1, meterBoxSizeX/2-chsize, -meterBoxSizeY/2, 1, meterBoxSizeX/2, -meterBoxSizeY/2+chsize, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
LINE2 meterBoxSizeX/2, meterBoxSizeY/2-chsize, -meterBoxSizeX/2, meterBoxSizeY/2-chsize LINE2 meterBoxSizeX/2, -meterBoxSizeY/2+chsize, -meterBoxSizeX/2, -meterBoxSizeY/2+chsize
IF withHouse THEN DRAWINDEX 20
PUT A/2, B/2, 1, -A/2, B/2, 1, -A/2, -B/2, 1, A/2, -B/2, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF ENDIF
DRAWINDEX 10
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 5, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 5 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Gas Meter
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
chsize = meterBoxSizeY/7
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z
Symbol.Script_UI:
! Gas Meter
UI_DIALOG `Специальные Параметры MEP`
DIM ui_vis_str[1][2] ui_vis_str[1][1] = `Корпус` ui_vis_str[1][2] = "HouseMaterial"
DIM ui_vis_attr[5][4] FOR i = 1 TO 5 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ui_vis_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_vis_attr[1][1] = 3 ui_vis_attr[1][2] = 1 ui_vis_attr[1][3] = 7 ui_vis_attr[1][4] = 0
ui_vis_attr[2][1] = 1 ui_vis_attr[2][2] = 237 ui_vis_attr[2][3] = 68 ui_vis_attr[2][4] = 14
ui_vis_attr[5][2] = 0 IF NOT(withHouse) THEN ui_vis_attr[5][2] = 4
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS ALL ui_vis_str = ui_vis_str, ui_vis_attr = ui_vis_attr, ui_centerline_vars = 0, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Gas Meter
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
IF NOT(withHouse) THEN LOCK "HouseMaterial", "isCovered"
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "withHouse" THEN IF withHouse THEN A = houseSizeX B = houseSizeY ZZYZX = houseSizeZ ELSE A = meterBoxSizeX B = meterBoxSizeY ZZYZX = meterBoxSizeZ ENDIF
PARAMETERS A = A PARAMETERS B = B PARAMETERS ZZYZX = ZZYZX ENDIF
IF withHouse THEN VALUES "A" RANGE (meterBoxSizeX, ] VALUES "B" RANGE (meterBoxSizeY, ] VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE (meterBoxSizeZ, ]
houseSizeX = A houseSizeY = B houseSizeZ = ZZYZX PARAMETERS houseSizeX = houseSizeX PARAMETERS houseSizeY = houseSizeY PARAMETERS houseSizeZ = houseSizeZ ELSE VALUES "meterBoxSizeX" RANGE [chsize*3, ] VALUES "meterBoxSizeY" RANGE [0.01, ] VALUES "meterBoxSizeZ" RANGE [chsize*3, ]
VALUES "A" RANGE [chsize*3, ] VALUES "B" RANGE [0.01, ] VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [chsize*3, ]
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" THEN meterBoxSizeX = A PARAMETERS meterBoxSizeX = meterBoxSizeX ELSE IF ABS(A - meterBoxSizeX) > EPS THEN A = meterBoxSizeX PARAMETERS A = A ENDIF ENDIF IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" THEN meterBoxSizeY = B PARAMETERS meterBoxSizeY = meterBoxSizeY ELSE IF ABS(B - meterBoxSizeX) > EPS THEN B = meterBoxSizeY PARAMETERS B = B ENDIF ENDIF IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ZZYZX" THEN meterBoxSizeZ = ZZYZX PARAMETERS meterBoxSizeZ = meterBoxSizeZ ELSE IF ABS(ZZYZX - meterBoxSizeZ) > EPS THEN ZZYZX = meterBoxSizeZ PARAMETERS ZZYZX = ZZYZX ENDIF ENDIF ENDIF ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 2
! --- 1st CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Труба Впускного Соединения `
ConDVecX = 0 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 1
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = 1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, MIN(meterBoxSizeX, meterBoxSizeY-chsize*2)] PARAMETERS ConDepth_1 = ConWidth_1 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_1" VALUES "ConLength_1" RANGE [0, ]
VALUES "ConPosX_1" RANGE [-meterBoxSizeX/2+ConWidth_1/2, meterBoxSizeX/2-ConWidth_1/2] VALUES "ConPosY_1" RANGE [-meterBoxSizeY/2+chsize+ConWidth_1/2, meterBoxSizeY/2-chsize-ConWidth_1/2] PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = ZZYZX/2+meterBoxSizeZ/2 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
! --- 2nd CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 2 ConName = `Труба Выпускного Соединения`
ConDVecX = 0 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 1
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = 1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "ConWidth_2" RANGE (0, MIN(meterBoxSizeX, meterBoxSizeY-chsize*2)] PARAMETERS ConDepth_2 = ConWidth_2 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_2" VALUES "ConLength_2" RANGE [0, ]
VALUES "ConPosX_2" RANGE [-meterBoxSizeX/2+ConWidth_2/2, meterBoxSizeX/2-ConWidth_2/2] VALUES "ConPosY_2" RANGE [-meterBoxSizeY/2+chsize+ConWidth_2/2, meterBoxSizeY/2-chsize-ConWidth_2/2] PARAMETERS ConPosZ_2 = ZZYZX/2+meterBoxSizeZ/2 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_2, ConPosY = ConPosY_2, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_2, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_2, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_2, ConWidth = ConWidth_2, ConDepth = ConDepth_2, ConLength = ConLength_2, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_2, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_2, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_2, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_2, ConToolType = ConToolType_2, ConStatus = ConStatus_2, ConType_2 = ConType_2, ConConnectorType_2 = ConConnectorType_2, ConSystem_2 = ConSystem_2, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_2, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
